item.title: Differences in MacOS & Linux command
item.description: echo Useful commands Git related use history command: history ! + number of the past command removed cached folder when submodule Submodule: git submodule add url_to_repo projectfolder Removed cached folder: git rm --cached projectfolder crtl+A: start of a command, crtl+E: end of a command clear all pycache in current directory: find . -name '__pycache__' -type d -exec rm -rf {} \; clear all .
